{"tid":263930,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得我女朋友呃緊我","createTime":"2017-05-30T12:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T13:26:32.000Z","uid":93917,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"877c03ec9211b1d498c2c7ec3784aa860e43d32b","tid":263930,"uid":93917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:00:07.000Z","msg":"利申：借朋友ac開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同佢識咗兩個禮拜左右<br />\n佢本身有一個男朋友<br />\n但係佢就話幾鍾意我想同我一齊<br />\n有提過話想我做佢既ptbf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為佢男朋友對佢好衰<br />\n同時每次佢想分手都會喊打喊殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直到今日佢都唔敢同佢男朋友講分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底佢係咪呃緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6fc9440bae24da9e4d64db380dbe249cd30f06","tid":263930,"uid":77643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"留名！！"},{"pid":"c8513729ff5070c88a9779ad941c1046b75be468","tid":263930,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:01:50.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"ee66c2b751ee2bfaad2009aa26ae63b3e41358d8","tid":263930,"uid":93917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名！！</blockquote><br />\n我唔係好友二號呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37edbc7b89bf2e28506af485a30e2d2481208183","tid":263930,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:02:39.000Z","msg":"你肯定佢係你女朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf3a1b9e0216a87d32cadfd1dcd675cdbe1d559","tid":263930,"uid":93917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:03:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你肯定佢係你女朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話佢係架...<img src=\"/a